# ResQLink Environment Variables - Example File
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Rename this file to `.env` or duplicate it as `.env`
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual API keys
# 3. Restart the development server (`npm run dev`) for the changes to take effect

# 1. What3Words
# Get your API key at: https://developer.what3words.com
VITE_WHAT3WORDS_KEY=your_what3words_api_key_here

# 2. IQAir (AirVisual)
# Get your API key at: https://www.iqair.com/dashboard/api
VITE_IQAIR_KEY=your_iqair_api_key_here

# 3. Google Gemini AI
# Get your API key at: https://aistudio.google.com
VITE_GEMINI_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
